@startuml uc-4_moves_abilities
!include ../../_theme.iuml

title UC-4 — Review moves and abilities

|Student|
start
:Select a species or instance;
|System|
:Gather `learnset.moves_by_level` and `possible_abilities`
(species scope)
or `move_slots` and `chosen_ability` (instance scope);
:Serialize to the Moves/Abilities tab payload;
|Student|
:Press `]` (or click) to focus Moves/Abilities tab;
|System|
:Display moves, categories, types, and ability effects;
|Student|
if (Inspect a specific ability?) then (yes)
    :Click the class name in relationships;
    |System|
    :Focus UML on `PassiveAbility` / `TriggeredAbility`;
endif
stop

@enduml
